<asp:Content ID="Content2" ContentPlaceHolderID="ContentPlaceHolder1" runat="server">
    <!-- ****#RETURN POLICY#**** -->
    <section>
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <h1 class="title text-center text-uppercase my-5" style="color: #726a95;">Return Policy</h1>
            <div class="m-5" align="justify">
                <h5 class="text-capitalize lh-lg"> 
                    Return Policy
                </h5>
                <p>
                    At XBook, we want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase. If for any reason you are not satisfied, you may return the product for a full refund within [30] days of receipt.
                </p>
                <p>
                    To be eligible for a return, the product must be in its original condition and packaging. Books must be unopened and undamaged, and all other products must be unused and in their original packaging.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Please note that we cannot accept returns of certain products, such as e-books or items that are personalized or customized for you.
                </p>
                <p>
                    To request a return, please contact us at [contact information] with your order number and the reason for the return. We will provide you with instructions on how to return the product to us.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Return shipping costs are the responsibility of the customer unless the product is defective or the return is the result of our error. In such cases, we will cover the cost of return shipping.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We will process your return and issue a refund as soon as we receive and inspect the returned product. Please allow up to [14] business days for the refund to be credited to your original method of payment.
                </p>
                <p>
                    If you have any questions about our return policy or the return process, please don't hesitate to <a href="Contact.aspx" class="link-primary">contact us</a>. We are here to help!                
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</asp:Content>
